🚀 WorkflowEvent kya hai?
👉 WorkflowEvent SailPoint me ek concept hai, na ki commonly use hone wali direct class (like Identity, Task, etc.)
👉 Iska matlab:-
Workflow ke andar hone wale events / actions / state changes.

🔥 Workflow ke andar kaun-kaun se events hote hain:-
Event	                  Condition	                       Method (kis object ka)
Workflow Started	wfCase.getState().equals("Running")	    WorkflowCase
Workflow Completed	wfCase.getState().equals("Completed")	WorkflowCase
Workflow Rejected	wfCase.getState().equals("Rejected")	WorkflowCase
Step Entered	    step execute hua	                    WorkflowCase
Step Completed	    step finish hua	                        WorkflowCase
Approval Triggered	approval step aaya	                     WorkItem
WorkItem Created	workItem != null	                     WorkItem

